{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, the only time we ever got out of barracks was to do some individual training ourselves or to go to the castle and fire a salute when some dignitary or some warship came into the Firth or Forth.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But nobody ever thought-- this was 1934-- nobody ever thought of exercising with infantry, what we call all arms training.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was five years before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we weren't very-- we weren't very militaristic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And nobody seemed to really mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It wasn't until we actually left Edinburgh and came down to Aldershot Command that we met a different world, where clearly-- this was 1936 and the things were happening on the continent and in Germany where people who could think, they had realized that war was in the offing.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we started working with the infantry and everybody else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we weren't very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we got better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't really mean very much but, it was 835724.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know-- I only kept that as long as I was in the ranks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was commissioned, they gave me another number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I joined in Edinburgh a regiment which was number 16.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a regular field regiment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed with them and went to France with them in September 1939.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I came home from France and I was put into an officer's training school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I rejoined that regiment when it came back from Dunkirk and I was with them only for a very short time and then I went off as a reinforcement to a regiment which had no training at all.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then eventually, I went to Special Forces, which was the Mountain Artillery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that will bring us up to 1941-42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kristanna?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
